  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check: confirm working tree clean, branch is `work/ai-spaarke-action-engine-r1`, baseline build passes. Confirm task 040 (ActionEndpoints.cs) shows ✅ in TASK-INDEX.md AND task 042 (ScheduledActionDispatchJobHandler.cs) status (if ✅, this task edits it; if not yet, document the dependency). (task-execute Step 0)</step>
